<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10561657>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Grotea delicator. A. habitus in lateral view; B. head in postero-ventrolateral view, detail of projection of gena (close to the junction of occipital and hypostomal carinae); C. prothorax in dorsal view, detail on the anterior margin impressed and strongly reflexed; D. hind wing, detail of the distribution of distal hamuli on vein RA. Scale bar in mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10561657/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

